<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;action=profile;u=76071" title="检视会员资料:  丞相">丞相</a>
</h4>
<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_937905_extra_info">
<li class="title">银渡鸦<li class="postgroup">Chivary<li class="stars"><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><li class="postcount">帖子数: 1518<li class="karma">苹果币: 5<li class="blurb">还算可以的玩家，以及不行的GM<li class="profile">
